# RIA red-status JSON emission directory.
#
# Per RIA architecture v2 §5.6 schema v1.1, every commit to RIA `main`
# emits `<sha>.json` here describing tests blocked by platform gaps.
#
# Emitter: ria/observability/red_status.py (sub-wave 3 deliverable).
# Mapping: tests/_blocked_by_platform.yaml.
#
# This file exists to ensure the directory survives `git add` until the
# first JSON is emitted in sub-wave 3.
